name: Honoka Kousaka - Love Live!
description:
Please don't use "from behind" in prompt or anything similar, because have bugs with "one side up" tag, sorry for that, when i find a new way to optimize these glitches i will update.

Weight is your choice, but i like 0.5

Tags you'll need: 1girl, solo, kousaka honoka, yellow hair bow, one side up, orange hair, blue eyes, medium hair,

if you can add two side up in negative prompt, but i don't used this before.

If you like my LoRAs, please support me on ko-fi

Follow me on pixiv

Please comment what you want to see next (main characters of lovelive! )
